relation: Darrow2 - #86 A few harsh words is all it takes to bring Giygas to the breaking point and finally, at long last, we see his true self appear.
Darrow2 - #87 The Universal Cosmic Destroyer emerges at last. The madness is no longer containable, nor is there any escape from it.

Darrow2 - #88 Fear begins to set in as Jeff and Ness start to realize just how helpless this battle is becoming. For Jeff, there is still resistance, but Ness is too easily broken after recent events.
Darrow2 - #89 A horrible turn of fate brings disaster upon Ness, who collapses as a result of the mental shock. With Jeff all alone, the battle grows even more hopeless.
Darrow - #29 Frank's mobile armor, Frankystein Mark II enters the battle. Although it looks like wood, it's actually made out of a rare metal called Frankarium. Seriously!
